62
00:04:47,849 --> 00:04:51,506
Exactly. I wonder why.

63
00:04:51,506 --> 00:04:53,393
What?

64
00:04:53,393 --> 00:04:55,154
Why does he do that

65
00:04:56,080 --> 00:04:58,614
