- Yes.

73
00:05:25,694 --> 00:05:27,363
Who is it?

74
00:05:28,689 --> 00:05:30,928
I'll introduce him to you later.

75
00:05:42,085 --> 00:05:43,923
You guys go ahead. I'll catch up.

76
00:05:43,923 --> 00:05:45,178
