93
00:06:42,302 --> 00:06:44,730
Am I some kind of exception? Why?

94
00:06:44,730 --> 00:06:47,782
It's nice to be polite.

95
00:06:47,782 --> 00:06:52,072
A gentleman is polite to even those

96
