108
00:07:21,021 --> 00:07:22,383
Right?

109
00:07:25,694 --> 00:07:29,029
If what's inside isn't that great, at least the packaging should look nice.

110
00:07:29,029 --> 00:07:31,097
That's why I picked

111
00:07:31,097 --> 00:07:32,889
