169
00:13:08,019 --> 00:13:10,873
- Yes, did anything happen?
- No.

170
00:13:45,408 --> 00:13:47,619
♪ For you ♪

171
00:13:49,162 --> 00:13:53,005
♪ The first time I saw you, ♪

172
00:13:53,005 --> 00:14:00,089
