207
00:16:37,719 --> 00:16:39,214
Scared?

208
00:16:40,249 --> 00:16:42,608
Being on the rooftop with me.

209
00:16:42,608 --> 00:16:44,589
And?

210
00:16:44,589 --> 00:16:47,660
